
v1.2. Support searching with empty query. Most keys are now singular strings (plural only if they *require* an Array value). Verbs have been un-nouned ('concatenate', not 'concats'; 'include', not 'includes'). 'filter', not 'raw_filters'; 'class_name', not 'model'. Finally, use a 'query' keypair instead of the first parameter to Ultrasphinx::Search.new for the query string (this simplifies form helpers).

v1.1. Parser rewrite and tests.

v1. Documentation; refactoring.

v0. Spike.
